sequenceDiagram
    participant Data as Ordered candles
    participant Indicator as Indicator engine
    participant Decision as Decision layer
    participant Runtime as Bot runtime
    participant Ledger as Event ledger
    participant Views as BotLens / reports

    Data->>Indicator: bar(t)
    Indicator->>Indicator: apply_bar(t)
    Indicator-->>Decision: snapshot outputs known_at=t
    Decision-->>Runtime: decision artifact for t
    Runtime->>Runtime: resolve execution effects
    Runtime-->>Ledger: append runtime/domain events
    Ledger-->>Views: rebuild projections and datasets

    Note over Indicator,Runtime: No downstream layer may use an artifact before its known_at time.
